headline: Medtronic (MDT) Q2 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Medtronic (MDT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +3.82% and +1.11%, respectively, for the quarter ended October 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
